            <Description>This dataset contains measurements high resolution snapshots of the ion 
                emission current from the ASPOC experiment on the Cluster C3 spacecraft. 
                Each Cluster spacecraft carries an identical an ASPOC (Active Spacecraft Potential Control) 
                experiment. ASPOC controls the electric potential of the Cluster spacecraft by means of an 
                ion beam. This modification of the charge balance improves the plasma measurements on board.
            </Description>
